metadata.name: BPVw #1
metadata.description: BopoVerse Women collection is a collection of 7,777 unique NFT collectibles living on the Ethereum blockchain. More than an NFT, BPVw is an artistic statement and a global status symbol for body positivity, self-love, and empowerment in the face of cyberbullying and body shaming. Your BPVw grants you exclusive access to the BopoVerse CLUB, get access to member-only events and perks, help form our impact, and become a part of the first all-inclusive community. Visit www.BopoVerse.com for more.
